35
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">究竟是只有阿良良木家这样</font>

36
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:49,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还是整个小镇都变成这样了</font>

37
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我觉得没必要确认了</font>

38
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是不确认不行</font>

39
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾等有那份责任</font>

40
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:01,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">之后我们不仅检查了周围邻居家</font>

41
