<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是说都怪你…</font>

49
00:03:21,890 --> 00:03:22,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不知不觉地）</font>

50
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都怪汝救了…</font>

51
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:23,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（将责任）</font>

52
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有充分准备就…</font>

53
00:03:24,290 --> 00:03:25,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个迷路小鬼…</font>

54
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:24,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（互相推卸）</font>

55
00:03:25,010 --> 00:03:26,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">进行时间跳跃…</font>

56
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:25,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（毫无责任感）</font>

57
00:03:25,610 --> 00:03:26,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（丑陋的）</font>

58
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:26,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">历史…</font>

59
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">历史…</font>

60
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:27,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（二人组）</font>

61
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因此而改变…</font>

62
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因此而改变…</font>

63
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:28,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">看来只能…</font>

64
00:03:28,540 --> 00:03:30,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">毫无疑问就是…</font>

65
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:29,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（在此）</font>

66
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这么解释…</font>

67
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样…</font>

68
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不行了  世界毁灭</font>

69
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:39,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">规模太大了  一点实感都没有</font>

70
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:42,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">打击太大  连恐慌的力气都没了</font>

71
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">明明火怜和月火都失踪了</font>

72
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:49,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">明明战场原  羽川  神原  千石也都不见了</font>

73
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:54,000
