93
00:05:05,910 --> 00:05:06,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（大概这个推理没有错误）</font>

94
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（小忍在思考着什么）</font>

95
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:11,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么了  小忍</font>

96
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:16,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾似乎想起了什么  但是现在还没有想清楚</font>

97
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:19,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾的记忆力还是太废了</font>

98
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:23,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么  有头绪了吗</font>

99
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:24,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（看来）</font>

100
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">关于世界变成这样的原因</font>

101
00:05:24,060 --> 00:05:25,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（她只是正在烦恼）</font>

102
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:30,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果我的判断是对的话  关于把这个世界变成这样的怪异</font>

103
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:34,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  是这样吧</font>

104
00:05:35,770 --> 00:05:40,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">姑且还是有收获的  至少知道了世界毁灭的时间</font>

105
00:05:40,490 --> 00:05:45,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  但是问题在于那天那个夜晚  到底发生了什么</font>

106
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:48,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这些不了解清楚的话就没法解决问题了</font>

107
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:53,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">解决问题？汝面对这种情况还准备解决什么问题</font>

108
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:57,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说是类似于神隐的状况的话</font>

109
00:05:57,730 --> 00:06:02,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要解决了怪异问题  大家就都能回到这个世界了吧</font>

110
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:02,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（虽然不是很清楚）</font>

111
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:05,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算不能填补这两个月的空白</font>

112
00:06:06,090 --> 00:06:08,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但一定能把世界恢复原样的</font>

113
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:09,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是  还是有希望的）</font>

114
00:06:10,010 --> 00:06:12,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以我想知道世界毁灭的原因</font>

115
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:14,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗</font>

116
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么我们就去调查原因吧</font>

117
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:23,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再回到过去一次  跳跃到6月14日的夜晚</font>

118
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:25,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就能搞清楚到底发生了什么</font>

119
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:34,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么了？</font>

120
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">能量一点也没剩</font>

121
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:42,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样啊</font>

122
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:44,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">原因就是…</font>

123
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:46,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个东西吧</font>

124
00:06:47,330 --> 00:06:48,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？这不就是…</font>

125
00:06:48,730 --> 00:06:48,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（回想）</font>

126
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个符不一样啊</font>

127
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到底是怎么回事啊</font>

128
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:58,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说种类不同  不如说是效果不同</font>

129
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:01,180
