135
00:07:18,130 --> 00:07:22,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝之前贴的符是用来防止灵力聚集的驱散剂</font>

136
00:07:23,290 --> 00:07:27,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而现在在吾眼前的符是用来吸收灵力的符</font>

137
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（用来时间跳跃的灵力）</font>

138
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就这样被吸收了）</font>

139
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吸收？</font>

140
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:31,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这样一来就回不到过去了啊）</font>

141
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:36,180
