142
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:40,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是从防止妖精大战的角度来说  结果是一样的</font>

143
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:42,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也是啊</font>

144
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:42,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就像是迁怒般）</font>

145
00:07:43,610 --> 00:07:48,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我知道这样说会有人错误地理解成我想要推卸自己的责任</font>

146
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:52,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但反正也没人听到  那就想说什么就说什么吧</font>

147
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">瞧你都干了什么好事啊  忍野！</font>

148
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还真是想说什么就说什么</font>

149
00:07:58,140 --> 00:08:02,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对于夏威夷衫小鬼来说使用什么符都是一样的</font>

150
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:08,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  他可不是随便到能凭感觉来决定大事的人</font>

151
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:12,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我想一定有什么只在这个历史上才成立的必然理由</font>

152
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:16,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是要追究那个理由的话  现在也已经没有意义了</font>

153
00:08:16,370 --> 00:08:17,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊</font>

154
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:22,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">唉  这样的话索性扔点香钱拜托神明算了</font>

155
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  等等</font>

156
00:08:24,490 --> 00:08:27,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把这个符剥下来的话  之后只要等待一段时间</font>

157
00:08:28,130 --> 00:08:31,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这里不就又能重新积攒灵力了吗</font>

158
00:08:31,850 --> 00:08:32,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说汝啊！</font>

159
00:08:33,210 --> 00:08:33,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吸收）</font>

160
00:08:33,910 --> 00:08:34,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吞噬）</font>

161
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个符不是汝能…</font>

162
00:08:40,170 --> 00:08:45,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  就像吾所说  类似于怪异的事物是不可以触碰这种符的</font>

163
00:08:49,370 --> 00:08:52,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样啊  真是绝望啊</font>

164
00:08:52,650 --> 00:08:54,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然绝望啊</font>

165
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">这…这是什么啊</font>

166
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（腐烂了的尸体）</font>

167
00:09:07,570 --> 00:09:08,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">丧尸</font>

168
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:11,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（永远持续着死亡的尸体）</font>

169
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝不要动  看来站在这里的话  它们就暂时不能接近</font>

170
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:16,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">汝不要动  看来站在这里的话  它们就暂时不能接近</font>

171
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">嗯…啊</font>

172
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">怎么会变成这样</font>

173
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:22,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">另外为什么它们不再继续靠近呢</font>

174
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">是因为这张符啊</font>

175
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:29,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">这些家伙知道只能靠近到这里  再进一步的话就会有危险</font>

176
00:09:29,650 --> 00:09:30,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">它们竟然会知道？</font>

177
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:31,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">总之</font>

178
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:35,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">趁着符还有灵效  赶紧从这里撤退吧</font>

179
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:40,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">哎…撤退？  站在这里不就是安全的吗？</font>

180
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:44,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">就像汝所见  它们的数量正在不断增加</font>

181
00:09:44,810 --> 00:09:46,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">说实话这状况吾也看不懂</font>

182
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:52,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">怎么说呢…只要对方是怪异就不可能是吾和汝的对手</font>

183
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:55,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">不过考虑到这些有可能是用镇上居民的尸体制成的丧尸</font>

184
00:09:55,730 --> 00:09:57,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">这样一来我们也不能糊里糊涂地去驱散它们</font>

185
00:09:57,770 --> 00:09:58,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">是啊</font>

186
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:01,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">所以现在先撤退  汝</font>

187
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:15,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">姑且算是逃脱成功了</font>

188
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:18,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">嗯  但是它们到底是怎么了</font>

189
00:10:18,890 --> 00:10:22,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">不知道  但是它们与其说是丧尸  倒不如说是…</font>

190
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:34,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">怎么会这样</font>

191
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:38,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">看来我们犯下了一个无从寻找借口并无法弥补的大错</font>

192
00:10:39,130 --> 00:10:44,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">就是因为我通过时间跳跃改变了过去  竟然将全人类变成了丧尸</font>

193
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:50,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">不  汝啊  这并不是需要汝烦恼的事</font>

194
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:53,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">都是吾的错  这一切都是吾的错</font>

195
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:57,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">这是怎么回事  你能这么说我很高兴</font>

196
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">但是小忍  因为这是我…</font>

197
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:07,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">不  这不是在包庇你  这是严肃的事实  残酷的现实</font>

198
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:08,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">小忍</font>

199
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:14,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">汝听好了  首先  这不是丧尸  而是吸血鬼的穷途末路啊</font>

200
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:15,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吸——血鬼？）</font>

201
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:18,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">吸血鬼？</font>

202
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:21,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">应该说它们和你一样</font>

203
00:11:22,450 --> 00:11:27,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">因为它们都是和你一样  被吾变成吸血鬼的原人类啊</font>

204
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:28,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（原）</font>

205
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:28,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（人）</font>

206
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:28,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（类）</font>

207
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:31,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">被你…？</font>

208
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:31,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">没错</font>

209
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:37,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">也就是说  在这个历史里  毁灭这个世界的…</font>

210
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#c0c0c0">就是吾</font>

211
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:54,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">就这样我们保持在三百米的高度  等待着黎明的到来</font>

212
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45" color="#808080">然后到了黎明之时</font>

213
00:11:57,020 --> 00:12:02,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从太阳从东方升起的那一刻起  地面上的僵尸群便变得无影无踪</font>

214
00:12:05,010 --> 00:12:09,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说…你说是你的错又是怎么回事  告诉我</font>

215
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:15,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都是吾的错…准确说是这个历史上的吾的错</font>

216
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:19,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个历史…是指已经改变的…</font>

217
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:24,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被我们改变的这个历史中的忍野忍吗</font>

218
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:29,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  这个世界的吾  那个不是吾的吾在两个月前</font>

219
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:31,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把全人类都变成了吸血鬼</font>

220
00:12:32,370 --> 00:12:33,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是这么回事</font>

221
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">6月14日</font>

222
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？</font>

223
00:12:37,330 --> 00:12:40,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那一天是什么日子  刚才总算想起来了</font>

224
00:12:41,340 --> 00:12:43,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那一天是什么日子…？</font>

225
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:48,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝也应该记得吧  那么印象深刻的一天</font>

226
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想不起什么来吗</font>

227
00:12:50,930 --> 00:12:55,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个…世界毁灭的日子当然印象深刻了</font>

228
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:59,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">6月14日的晚上或者说6月15日…</font>

229
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:05,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不对不对  不是这样  是原本的…原来历史中的6月14日晚上</font>

230
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:07,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">6月14日吗…</font>

231
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">14日  14日…</font>

232
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:14,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为14日是星期三所以15日是星期四…</font>

233
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:16,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">看来是想不起来了啊</font>

234
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:23,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说6月15日是文化节的前日  这么说汝应该能明白吧</font>

235
00:13:27,930 --> 00:13:29,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">看来是注意到了呢</font>

236
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:30,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊…</font>

237
00:13:31,410 --> 00:13:35,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好差劲的男人  和恋人第一次约会的日子</font>

238
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:37,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">平时把人家叫成恩人恩人的</font>

239
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:40,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">人家前班长出那么大事的日子</font>

240
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:41,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还有吾离家出走的日子</font>

241
00:13:42,210 --> 00:13:44,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还有夏威夷衫小鬼离开的日子</font>

242
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:47,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">居然全部打包忘了个一干二净</font>

243
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:54,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可是…那些又和现在的局面有什么联系  我还是不明白</font>

244
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:59,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">确实发生了很多事情  但世界也不该就因此而毁灭吧</font>

245
00:14:00,290 --> 00:14:04,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">硬要说的话  黑羽川的跳梁跋扈确实和怪异现象有关</font>

246
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:09,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不…黑羽川虽然在现象上并非于此无关</font>

247
00:14:10,410 --> 00:14:12,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但重要的是吾的离家出走</font>

248
00:14:13,410 --> 00:14:17,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你的离家出走？但那不是顺利解决了…</font>

249
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:25,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不对  顺利解决的只是在我们所知所经历的那个历史</font>

250
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:29,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是说在这个历史中还是因为发生了什么事情</font>

251
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:31,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果最终没有解决吗</font>

252
00:14:34,930 --> 00:14:40,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果吾一直也没把那次离家出走的详细原因对汝讲过</font>

253
00:14:40,770 --> 00:14:43,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝也刻意没有向吾深究</font>

254
00:14:43,810 --> 00:14:49,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾很感激汝的善解人意  在这里也不打算对汝细说</font>

255
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:53,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  现在有一个无法隐瞒的事实不得不说了</font>

256
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哦  那就别卖关子了</font>

257
00:14:57,100 --> 00:15:02,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那一天的吾曾想  如果汝找不到吾  吾就毁灭世界</font>

258
00:15:03,170 --> 00:15:05,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那事有那么严重吗！</font>

259
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:06,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为…为什么？</font>

260
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:11,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">自暴自弃…或者说是迁怒于人吧  从各种角度来说</font>

261
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:18,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是说这个世界的…还真是麻烦  这个历史的阿良良木历</font>

262
00:15:19,010 --> 00:15:23,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那个6月14日没能找到你吗</font>

263
00:15:24,050 --> 00:15:26,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">应该就是这么回事吧</font>

264
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:29,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想想看吧  说起来那一天</font>

265
00:15:29,740 --> 00:15:33,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">首先发现吾离家的不正是那个迷路小鬼吗</font>

266
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:37,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  不仅仅是那一天</font>

267
00:15:38,090 --> 00:15:41,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果没有八九寺  如果没有身为怪异的八九寺</font>

268
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:44,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">别说6月14日  就连那个母亲节</font>

269
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我都不会遇到八九寺</font>

270
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:52,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说  这个世界的阿良良木历是没有遇见过八九寺的阿良良木历</font>

271
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:59,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗…那我那时八成已经被黑羽川杀掉了</font>

272
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:05,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小忍  这个问题你不愿回答也可以不回答</font>

273
00:16:05,810 --> 00:16:08,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以相当轻率的感觉听我说也无所谓</font>

274
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:14,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这已经是我没有想过  甚至连想都不愿再想的问题  如何</font>

275
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:21,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我和你像这样  彼此间束缚的状态从春假就在持续</font>

276
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:24,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在这个状态下  不管我还是你</font>

277
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:27,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果一方因为什么不幸的事故而丧命的话</font>

278
00:16:28,290 --> 00:16:30,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">另一方又会怎么样呢</font>

279
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:34,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为彼此束缚  所以会一同丧命吗</font>

280
00:16:34,570 --> 00:16:35,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还是说会…</font>

281
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是「还是说」的那个</font>

282
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:42,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个大脑发育不良的猫女是决不会明白</font>

283
00:16:42,730 --> 00:16:45,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但那夏威夷衫小鬼的话应该能了解</font>

284
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:52,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝不也说过吗  只要抛弃吾  随时都能恢复成人类</font>

285
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:58,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么反过来说  只要把我杀了</font>

286
00:16:58,660 --> 00:17:02,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你就能恢复力量  变回传说中最强的吸血鬼之王</font>

287
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:06,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">铁血的  热血的  冷血的  吸血鬼</font>

288
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:08,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就能变回去了啊</font>

289
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:16,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而吾这次  是真心毁灭了世界</font>

290
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:25,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">具体说  就是把全镇  全日本乃至全世界的人类</font>

291
00:17:25,930 --> 00:17:27,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都变成了吸血鬼</font>

292
00:17:28,140 --> 00:17:30,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把人类都变成了吸血鬼</font>

293
00:17:31,610 --> 00:17:37,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实事实上吾去吸血的只是最初的几个人</font>

294
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:42,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而他们也就变成了和吾一样企图毁灭世界的吸血鬼</font>

295
00:17:42,450 --> 00:17:45,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再将周围的人类继续变成吸血鬼</font>

296
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:49,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样产生的吸血鬼论起来都是吾的眷属</font>

297
00:17:49,970 --> 00:17:53,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（下午六点至早上六点）</font>

298
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:53,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都是企图毁灭世界的吸血鬼</font>

299
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:58,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后他们就如老鼠繁衍一般以等比数列增殖</font>

300
00:17:58,160 --> 00:18:02,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">接着就在转眼间把世界…把人类这个种族毁灭了</font>

301
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:08,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但如果那么说的话  这里的我死了  你却没死</font>

302
00:18:09,420 --> 00:18:12,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那这个历史中的你现在又在哪里做着什么呢</font>

303
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个毁灭了世界的你…</font>

304
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:18,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可现在你就在这里</font>

305
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:25,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">恐怕这个历史中的吾已经死掉了</font>

306
00:18:26,080 --> 00:18:26,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">死…</font>

307
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:32,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不用多说了吧  全世界能杀掉吾的只有一个人</font>

308
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那就是吾自己</font>

309
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:36,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">换句话说  吾是自杀的</font>

310
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:45,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后因为吾的自杀  眷属们全部丧尸化了</font>

311
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:51,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说吸血鬼恢复成人类的办法  是亲手杀掉你</font>

312
00:18:52,330 --> 00:18:55,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但如果你本人死了  那恢复的办法也就化为了泡影</font>

313
00:18:56,730 --> 00:19:00,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只能任由吸血鬼的血失控了吗</font>

314
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:03,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对不起</font>

315
00:19:06,170 --> 00:19:12,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾并不是想要这样的结局  吾当时只是想被汝找到</font>

316
00:19:13,530 --> 00:19:17,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可是仅仅为了那小孩子闹脾气般的理由</font>

317
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:21,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就把汝宝贵的世界毁掉</font>

318
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:25,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">别说了</font>

319
00:19:27,090 --> 00:19:27,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不用道歉</font>

320
00:19:29,930 --> 00:19:31,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不要责备自己</font>

321
00:19:31,930 --> 00:19:35,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">的确  这个历史上的你也许是毁掉了这个历史</font>

322
00:19:36,410 --> 00:19:38,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但罪魁祸首是那个不是你的你</font>

323
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:43,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这…这么说是没错  但那还是吾</font>

324
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:47,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之小忍  不要再道歉了</font>

325
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:52,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你什么都没做错  至少现在在我面前的你是这样</font>

326
00:19:54,210 --> 00:19:57,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">接下来的日子  我们两个得在这个毁灭后的世界…</font>

327
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,810
<font face="@FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}（请在车门两侧让出空间  并排站立）</font>

328
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,810
<font face="@FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}（列车接近请注意）</font>

329
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在这个没有一个人存在的恐怖世界</font>

330
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:03,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">同时又有大量丧尸存在的梦魇般的世界</font>

331
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我们要在这样的世界里生存</font>

332
00:20:06,170 --> 00:20:08,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要比以前更进一步地彼此帮助了</font>

333
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:09,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝…</font>

334
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是小忍的错</font>

335
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:31,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝怎么了</font>

336
00:20:31,610 --> 00:20:33,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  这个…</font>

337
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:36,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我觉得有个办法可以试试</font>

338
00:20:39,170 --> 00:20:41,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">放那种东西又能怎样呢</font>

339
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:45,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过作为日本传统上宣告夏天结束的方式倒是不错</font>

340
00:20:45,900 --> 00:20:51,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  虽然我是很想和你一起享受夏天的烟花</font>

341
00:20:52,170 --> 00:20:55,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但在这个看似毁灭的世界  也许还有谁</font>

342
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:59,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过也只是说万一  可也许还会有幸存的家伙</font>

343
00:20:59,570 --> 00:21:03,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么说呢…就是畏惧晚上会出现的大量丧尸</font>

344
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而躲藏起来存活的家伙们</font>

345
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:05,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯</font>

346
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:08,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（三天后的下午）</font>

347
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:10,050
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为了能让焰火传得更远一些</font>

348
00:21:08,290 --> 00:21:09,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（烟花大会当天）</font>

349
00:21:09,290 --> 00:21:10,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这已是不能再期盼更多的）</font>

350
00:21:10,300 --> 00:21:11,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（最适合放焰火的天气）</font>

351
00:21:10,300 --> 00:21:13,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我选在一个阴天放焰火</font>

352
00:21:11,300 --> 00:21:12,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（三天后  阴）</font>

353
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:14,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（八月二十六日）</font>

354
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">玉屋呀</font>

355
00:21:21,970 --> 00:21:23,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">键屋呀</font>

356
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:32,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好了  这样一来到晚上之前就只有等待了</font>

357
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:33,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯</font>

358
00:21:33,530 --> 00:21:36,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之不要抱太多期待就是了</font>

359
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:41,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算万一有人克服困难存活下来</font>

360
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:44,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也未必会被烟花吸引而出现吧</font>

361
00:21:45,810 --> 00:21:48,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">人类可是已经被吸血鬼毁灭了</font>

362
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:50,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被认为是陷阱也是理所应当的</font>

363
00:21:50,820 --> 00:21:51,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且…</font>

364
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:52,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂</font>

365
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:57,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这点疼痛不至于喊那么大声吧</font>

366
00:21:57,960 --> 00:22:00,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">过度期待虽然不好</font>

367
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:03,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但过度悲观也会一事无成</font>

368
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:07,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其垂头丧气地等</font>

369
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:14,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还是去想想怎么和被吸引而来的人类交流吧</font>

370
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对方可不一定是女高中生啊</font>

371
00:22:17,760 --> 00:22:18,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊</font>

372
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:49,060
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}心臓に合わせて　本当の気持ちを</font>

373
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:49,060
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">贴近内心  用自己的声音</font>

374
00:22:49,130 --> 00:22:51,860
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}自分らしく　さあ　話そう</font>

375
00:22:49,130 --> 00:22:51,860
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">大胆说出真正的感情</font>

376
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:06,710
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}平凡な金曜日　落ち込んだ毎日は</font>

377
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:06,710
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">平凡的星期五  沮丧的每一天</font>

378
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:10,480
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}不安と後悔の連続</font>

379
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:10,480
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">充满无尽的不安和悔意</font>

380
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:16,840
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}作戦を考えて　この気持ちどうやって</font>

381
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:16,840
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">每天不停思考  用尽全部时间</font>

382
00:23:16,930 --> 00:23:20,020
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}言おうかなって今日も終わる</font>

383
00:23:16,930 --> 00:23:20,020
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">这份心意该如何表达</font>

384
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:26,460
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}君の目が泳いだら　不安でしょうがないんだよ</font>

385
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:26,460
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">每当你的眼神飘忽不定  我的心便满是不安</font>

386
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:31,640
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}知ってしちゃう　嫌だ嫌だって　渦巻いてたまらないんだ</font>

387
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:31,640
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">不想被你发觉  脑海中却一片混乱</font>

388
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:36,550
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}本当はね　ずっと君と二人だけがよかったんだ</font>

389
00:23:31,710 --> 00:23:36,550
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">其实我  只希望  能永远和你在一起</font>

390
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:41,620
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}純粋な愛の言葉　笑わないでよ　ねぇ</font>

391
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:41,620
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">这是我纯情的告白  请你认真对待</font>

392
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:46,660
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}きっとまたそんな君を諦めてやるもんかって</font>

393
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:46,660
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">或许我  还依然  无法轻易将你放弃</font>

394
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:51,880
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}必死に答えを探す　バカみたいだね  あぁ</font>

395
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:51,880
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">拼命寻找答案的我  实在太不聪明</font>

396
00:23:52,080 --> 00:23:56,770
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}目と目を合わせたら　怖がらずに　ほら</font>

397
